  "summary": "Malicious code in sensivity (npm)",
  "details": "Sensivity@2.5.38 follows the same delivery chain as sibling versions: launcher.js loads a heavily obfuscated server.obf.js (8K+ obfuscated identifiers) via eval(fs.readFileSync(...)) and self-spawns a detached process (process.execPath, detached:true) for stealth persistence. The self-spawn-daemon plus eval-decoded-obfuscated-JS pattern is a known malware delivery chain.",
